    },
    {
      "text": "You awake in a dimly lit cellar. The smell of damp earth fills the air. A heavy wooden door stands locked to the north. You don't remember who you are — but a worn pack rests beside you, a sword's hilt jutting from it. Whoever left you here left you your gear; best arm yourself before anything else. (Open the Inventory tab to equip your belongings.)"
    }
  ],
